Conclusion

While it was still relatively simple to achieve this, there were a few things we had to be careful of. Since this is pre-alpha/alpha stage, I‚Äôm sure some (if not all) of the issues mentioned here will be addressed by the time this is production ready. I‚Äôm really excited for Compose and how it shapes the future of Android development and the quality of apps that we will be able to create.

